---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';

const schema = [
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://seo-guildford.uk/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Services", "item": "https://seo-guildford.uk/services/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Free SEO Audit", "item": "https://seo-guildford.uk/free-seo-audit-guildford/" }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "WebPage",
    "name": "Free SEO Audit Guildford",
    "description": "Request a free SEO audit for your Guildford business. A considered site health check covering technical issues, local visibility, and search performance.",
    "url": "https://seo-guildford.uk/free-seo-audit-guildford/",
    "isPartOf": { "@type": "WebSite", "name": "SEO Guildford", "url": "https://seo-guildford.uk/" }
  },
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Service",
    "name": "Free SEO Audit",
    "description": "A free SEO health check for Guildford and Surrey businesses covering technical errors, local search visibility, and Google Business Profile status.",
    "provider": {
      "@type": "LocalBusiness",
      "name": "SEO Guildford",
      "email": "hello@seo-guildford.uk",
      "sameAs": [],
      "areaServed": { "@type": "City", "name": "Guildford" }
    },
    "areaServed": { "@type": "City", "name": "Guildford", "containedInPlace": { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Surrey" } },
    "offers": {
      "@type": "Offer",
      "price": "0",
      "priceCurrency": "GBP",
      "availability": "https://schema.org/InStock",
      "url": "https://seo-guildford.uk/free-seo-audit-guildford/"
    }
  },
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How long does the free SEO audit take?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "You will receive your audit report within two to three working days of submitting the form. The review itself takes around 45 minutes per site." }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Is the free audit genuinely without obligation?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "It is. There is no contract, no payment details required, and no obligation to purchase any services. The audit is a genuine site health check you can act on independently." }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What is the difference between the free audit and the comprehensive SEO audit?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "The free audit covers surface-level technical health, local visibility, and Google Business Profile status. The comprehensive audit (from £750) includes deep crawl analysis, backlink profiling, competitor benchmarking, content gap analysis, and a prioritised action plan with estimated ROI." }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Do you audit websites outside Guildford?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "The free audit is available to any business in Guildford, Woking, Godalming, Farnham, or the wider Surrey area. For businesses outside Surrey, please get in touch to discuss availability." }
      }
    ]
  }
];
---
<Base
  title="Free SEO Audit Guildford — Site Health Check"
  description="Request a free SEO audit for your Guildford business. A considered site health check covering technical issues, local visibility, and search rankings. No obligation."
  canonical="https://seo-guildford.uk/free-seo-audit-guildford/"
  schema={schema}
>
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <nav class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-6" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-brand">Home</a>
      <span class="mx-1">/</span>
      <a href="/services/" class="hover:text-brand">Services</a>
      <span class="mx-1">/</span>
      <span class="text-brand font-medium">Free SEO Audit</span>
    </nav>

    <div class="prose">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-brand mb-6">Free SEO Audit for Guildford Businesses</h1>

      <p>A free SEO audit gives Guildford business owners something deceptively simple yet remarkably valuable: a clear, evidence-based snapshot of how their website actually performs in Google search, which technical issues may be quietly constraining their visibility, and whether their local presence reflects the true potential of their business within the Surrey market.</p>

      <div class="quick-answer">
        <strong>The short version:</strong> Submit the form below to receive a free SEO health check within two to three working days. The audit covers technical errors, local search visibility, and Google Business Profile status. No payment details are required, there is no obligation, and no sales call unless you expressly request one.
      </div>

      <p>Most businesses along Guildford High Street, around Tunsgate Quarter, or operating near Surrey Research Park have never subjected their search presence to professional scrutiny -- which means fixable issues quietly accumulate, much like a slow leak in a roof. Broken links, missing metadata, unclaimed local listings, sluggish page speeds: each one bleeds a little visibility, and collectively they hand positions to competitors who have already done the work.</p>

      <p>This free audit is designed to change that. Whether you operate a gaming studio near the University of Surrey, a property agency listing homes across the GU postcode, or a healthcare practice close to Royal Surrey Hospital, the audit provides you with a factual, considered starting point.</p>

      <h2>What the Free Audit Includes</h2>

      <p>The free audit is a focused review rather than a full-depth analysis, covering the areas that matter most for identifying immediate opportunities:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Technical health scan</strong> -- crawl errors, broken links, page speed issues, and mobile usability problems that directly affect rankings</li>
        <li><strong>Local visibility check</strong> -- how your business appears in Google Maps and local pack results for your target area in Guildford and surrounding towns</li>
        <li><strong>Google Business Profile review</strong> -- whether your GBP listing is claimed, complete, and properly optimised for local search queries</li>
        <li><strong>On-page SEO snapshot</strong> -- title tags, meta descriptions, heading structure, and basic content issues on your most important pages</li>
        <li><strong>Competitor comparison</strong> -- a brief, considered look at how your search visibility compares to two direct competitors in your sector</li>
      </ul>

      <p>You receive a concise PDF report with findings and a clear explanation of what each issue means for your business.</p>

      <h2>Request Your Free Audit</h2>

      <p>Complete the form below and our team will review your site with the care it deserves. No automated tool outputs — every audit is conducted by hand.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Audit request form -->
    <form action="#" method="POST" class="bg-surface rounded-xl border border-border p-6 md:p-8 my-8 space-y-5">
      <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-2">All fields marked with * are required.</p>

      <div>
        <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-text mb-1">Name *</label>
        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required autocomplete="name" class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 rounded-md border border-border bg-white text-text focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand/30 focus:border-brand transition-colors" placeholder="Your full name" />
      </div>

      <div>
        <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-text mb-1">Email *</label>
        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required autocomplete="email" class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 rounded-md border border-border bg-white text-text focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand/30 focus:border-brand transition-colors" placeholder="you@example.co.uk" />
      </div>

      <div>
        <label for="website" class="block text-sm font-medium text-text mb-1">Website URL *</label>
        <input type="url" id="website" name="website" required autocomplete="url" class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 rounded-md border border-border bg-white text-text focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand/30 focus:border-brand transition-colors" placeholder="https://www.yourbusiness.co.uk" />
      </div>

      <div>
        <label for="business-type" class="block text-sm font-medium text-text mb-1">Business Type *</label>
        <select id="business-type" name="business_type" required class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 rounded-md border border-border bg-white text-text focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand/30 focus:border-brand transition-colors">
          <option value="" disabled selected>Select your sector</option>
          <option value="gaming-tech">Gaming / Technology</option>
          <option value="professional-services">Professional Services</option>
          <option value="property">Property / Estate Agency</option>
          <option value="healthcare">Healthcare</option>
          <option value="retail">Retail</option>
          <option value="hospitality">Hospitality</option>
          <option value="other">Other</option>
        </select>
      </div>

      <div>
        <label for="message" class="block text-sm font-medium text-text mb-1">Message (optional)</label>
        <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="3" class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 rounded-md border border-border bg-white text-text focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand/30 focus:border-brand transition-colors resize-y" placeholder="Tell us about your principal SEO goals or concerns"></textarea>
      </div>

      <button type="submit" class="cta-button w-full text-center">Request your audit</button>

      <p class="text-xs text-text-muted text-center">Your data is used solely to deliver the audit. No unsolicited correspondence, no mailing lists.</p>
    </form>
    <!-- End form -->

    <div class="prose">
      <h2>What Happens After You Submit</h2>

      <p>Once you submit the form, here is precisely what to expect:</p>

      <ol>
        <li><strong>Confirmation email</strong> -- you receive an acknowledgement within a few hours confirming your audit is in our queue</li>
        <li><strong>Manual review</strong> -- our team reviews your website by hand, checking technical health, local visibility, and on-page fundamentals with the thoroughness your business deserves</li>
        <li><strong>Report delivery</strong> -- within two to three working days, you receive a concise PDF report to your email with findings and recommended next steps</li>
        <li><strong>Optional follow-up call</strong> -- if you would like to discuss the findings, you may book a 15-minute call at no cost and with no obligation whatsoever</li>
      </ol>

      <p>The entire process is built around respect for your time. Guildford business owners are busy, analytical people with no patience for fluff -- so the report is written in clear, direct English that you can act on independently or hand to your developer with confidence.</p>

      <h2>How the Free Audit Differs from a Comprehensive SEO Audit</h2>

      <p>The free audit is a surface-level health check that catches the most apparent problems and provides a factual starting point. For businesses that need deeper insight, the <a href="/seo-audit-guildford/">comprehensive SEO audit</a> (from £750) goes significantly further.</p>

      <p>A comprehensive audit includes a complete technical crawl of every page, a backlink profile analysis, detailed competitor benchmarking against three to five rivals, a content gap analysis showing missed keyword opportunities, and a prioritised 90-day action plan with estimated traffic and revenue impact. It also covers AI search readiness, which is increasingly relevant for Guildford businesses competing in sectors like technology, property, and professional services.</p>

      <p>Think of the free audit as a preliminary consultation -- like a GP appointment that identifies whether you need a specialist. The comprehensive audit is that specialist investigation. Both are valuable, but they serve different purposes. Many clients start with the free version and commission the full audit once they see the scale of opportunity that data reveals.</p>

      <p>View the <a href="/seo-pricing-guildford/">full pricing breakdown</a> for all audit and retainer options.</p>

      <h2>Why Guildford Businesses Need an SEO Audit</h2>

      <p>Guildford is one of the most competitive local markets in the South East. With average property prices above £600,000, the customer lifetime value for businesses here is substantially higher than the national average, which makes search rankings disproportionately valuable.</p>

      <p>A single first-page ranking for a term like "solicitors Guildford" or "estate agents Guildford" can generate tens of thousands of pounds in annual revenue. An audit tells you precisely how far you are from those positions and what it will take to reach them.</p>

      <p>Businesses around Guildford Cathedral, the Friary Centre, and the University of Surrey campus serve affluent, digitally discerning customers who research thoroughly online before purchasing. If your site is not visible, those customers go to your competitors. The audit quantifies that gap with precision.</p>

      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How long does the free SEO audit take?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>You will receive your audit report within two to three working days of submitting the form. The review itself takes around 45 minutes per site, which is why each audit is conducted personally rather than through an automated tool.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Is the free audit genuinely without obligation?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>It is. There is no contract, no payment details required, and no obligation to purchase any services. The audit is a genuine site health check you can act on entirely independently. If you wish to discuss next steps, that is wholly your choice.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What is the difference between the free audit and the comprehensive SEO audit?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>The free audit covers surface-level technical health, local visibility, and Google Business Profile status. The <a href="/seo-audit-guildford/">comprehensive audit</a> (from £750) includes deep crawl analysis, backlink profiling, competitor benchmarking, content gap analysis, and a prioritised action plan with estimated ROI. The comprehensive version typically runs to 30 to 40 pages.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do you audit websites outside Guildford?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>The free audit is available to any business in Guildford, Woking, Godalming, Farnham, or the wider Surrey area. For businesses outside Surrey, please <a href="/contact/">get in touch</a> to discuss availability.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <h2>Next Steps</h2>

      <p>If you are ready to understand where your website stands, submit the form above. For businesses that already know they need ongoing SEO support, explore the <a href="/seo-pricing-guildford/">monthly retainer plans</a> or read about the full range of <a href="/services/">SEO services</a> available.</p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mt-8 not-prose">
        <a href="/seo-audit-guildford/" class="cta-button text-center">Comprehensive SEO Audit (£750)</a>
        <a href="/seo-pricing-guildford/" class="cta-button-outline text-center">View Pricing</a>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-text-muted">SEO Guildford is a considered search consultancy serving the Guildford area. Questions? Email <a href="mailto:hello@seo-guildford.uk">hello@seo-guildford.uk</a> or visit the <a href="/">homepage</a> to learn more about our approach.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>
